snippet.title: Natalie Brooks: The Treasures of the Lost Kingdom
snippet.description:
http://www.bigfishgames.com/download-games/4742/natalie-brooks-the-treasures-of-lost-kingdom/index.html
Famous teenage detective Natalie Brooks is back in an all-new adventure! In Treasures of the Lost Kingdom, Natalie faces the seemingly impossible task of saving her grandfather, a renowned archaeologist, from kidnappers holding him ransom for an ancient treasure map. She has just 24 hours to find the map, solve the mystery of a terrible curse and unmask the truth behind a legendary ghost train!
